sentences: Nandini Srikar (born 10 August 1969) is an Indian singer and performer.
In 1997, playback singer Hariharan heard her song and suggested to Vidyasagar that he hire her to sing for his upcoming film Uyirodu Uyiraga.
section: == Career ==

sentences: In 2001, she appeared on Mahmood Khan's album Panah.
section: == Career ==

sentences: In 2008, she worked with music director Dhruv Ghanekar with the vocal arrangements and harmonies for the songs in Drona.
section: == Career ==

sentences: Her debut solo album Beete Pal was released in 2011 in which she has composed, programmed, produced and performed all the songs.
section: == Career ==

sentences: In year 2016, she also worked for a Pakistani movie Hijrat (film) (directed by Farouq Mengal and produced by FM Productions).
section: == Career ==

sentences: In 2021, she collaborated with duo gardenstate in their song, “Aurora”.
